I am trying to watch updates to a calendar I created, but am not receiving e-mails when the calendar is updated. Other people receive emails without a problem. I have tried 'Send test email' through Adminisitration->Mail Servers which works just fine. I am also receiving e-mails when other pages I am watching are modified. I have tried to 'stop watching' and 'watch' again several times but to no avail. I also checked to see if leaving it at 'stop watching' would fix it (in case the bit was flipped) and that did not help either.

This is repeatable. I created a calendar with account A. When account B created new events, account A would *not* receive watch notifications. But when account A edited that calendar account B would receive emails. I tried with two accounts, two calendars.  

My workaround right now is that I created a new account which subscribes to the calendar. That new account is affiliated with a different e-mail address.

